➜这搭配绝了！鲜香配嫩滑，汤汁能下三碗饭！
http://www.sohu.com/a/437052912_100001467	14566
<p class="ql-align-center">秋冬需要多吃牛羊肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其中羊肉卷就深受大家的喜爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">既满足滋补，又满足方便快捷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但羊肉卷除了涮着吃还能用来炒着吃哦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天教大家做一道10分钟就能上桌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>洋葱泡菜搭配羊肉卷</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">﻿</span>好吃到舔盘的葱爆肥羊饭</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201208/f69e30ec28434a10b93cb4c08ce8a355.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">食材：羊肉卷 / 洋葱 /鸡蛋/西蓝花/红甜椒/ 料酒 / 生抽 / 蚝油 / 水淀粉 / 米饭 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201208/72daecef7ec14156999635952f7dcc0c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第一步：焯熟羊肉卷和蔬菜</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">锅内水煮开后倒点料酒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放入肥羊卷煮2分钟捞出备用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">西蓝花、红甜椒一起下沸水焯3分钟捞出备用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201208/7863277bdc314fb1adf20962bf5bf579.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第二步：炒配菜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">锅内热油放入洋葱丝爆香</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后放入肥羊卷翻炒一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放生抽、耗油、盐调味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201208/8312a919d75e45c7b660ed5953ef9d58.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第四步：放泡菜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">喜欢吃泡菜的亲可以加入点泡菜翻炒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样能让菜品味道更丰富</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果是给儿童吃可以跳过这一步</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201208/803bf3bf717449c2b3068b527404a4d6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翻炒均匀后即可出锅啦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">装一碗米饭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把煮好的西蓝花、红甜椒、荷包蛋放上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后夹一筷子色香味都一级棒的葱爆肥羊卷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放在米饭上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">顺带的汁水把米饭都浸染入味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201208/011f08148fa84af684dcadc3a090239f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">羊肉卷很蓬松</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">泡菜的颜色让肥羊卷看上去更诱人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其间点缀着洋葱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">香浓开胃~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201208/03aa566c296545cf8f8ccb89d9536039.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蓬松的羊肉再加上米饭，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">香浓可口又营养</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孩子都能多吃一碗饭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">简直不要太适合秋冬的家庭啦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个冬天，也可以温暖度过了。</p>
